image_analysis.description: A photograph of a long, narrow hallway with ornate wood paneling. The walls feature intricate marquetry or inlaid wood patterns in a geometric design. The floor is covered with a bright blue carpet featuring a dark border. A white protective cloth or tarp is partially covering the carpet in the foreground. There are several doorways visible leading into further rooms or corridors. A gold-framed mirror or picture frame is mounted on the left wall, with its center blacked out. Ornate, lantern-style light fixtures hang from the ceiling.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural photograph showing a perspective view down a hallway.
